metadata.name: Wild Dogs
metadata.description:
A wild pack of family dogs came running through the yard one day / My father got his gun, shot it up, they ran away, OK.
- Modest Mouse

I stayed in this house for a night on my way from Austin to Colorado, and in the morning, I got stuck with my dog a ways down the dirt road because two stray dogs were roaming around the yard... smelling everywhere my dog peed the night before.
